About MERmaid

MERmaid is a Music Emotion Recognition (MER) application from the{' '} MIR.CISUC team , part of the MERGE research project ( PTDC/CCI-COM/3171/2021 ). The system has been developed over the last years in a collaboration between{' '} CISUC {' '} (emotion recognition) and{' '} Ci2.ipt {' '} (software engineering part), with the purpose of illustrating the advances on this research topic, which usually stay buried in academic papers and do not reach the general public.
